      <title>1. Why FSM</title>
      <link>https://fsm-foundry.github.io/docs/docs/Concept/whyFsm/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://fsm-foundry.github.io/docs/docs/Concept/whyFsm/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Finite State Machine ( State Chart )&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-what-is-a-diagram&#34;&gt;1. What is a diagram&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#1-what-is-a-diagram&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A diagram is a visual model of behavior, structure, or flow — it helps people share understanding faster than plain text.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A good diagram is:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Visual&lt;/strong&gt; — gives a shared picture of behavior instead of only linear text&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Helpful&lt;/strong&gt; — improves understanding, communication, or analysis for a specific audience&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-visual-diagrams-are-better-than-text&#34;&gt;2. Visual Diagrams Are Better Than Text&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#2-visual-diagrams-are-better-than-text&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When complexity grows, text-based logic becomes hard to follow. Diagrams are better because:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2. Why FSM in Postgres</title>
      <link>https://fsm-foundry.github.io/docs/docs/Concept/whyFsmInPostgres/</link>
